text: The Mod Squad is an American crime drama series, originally broadcast for five seasons on ABC from September 24, 1968, to March 1, 1973. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * CBS Television Distribution Syndication Bible (including The Mod Squad) * Mod Squad Category:1960s American television series Category:1968 television series debuts Category:1973 American television series endings Category:1970s American television series Category:American crime drama television series Category:ABC network series
